# zgao11@illinois.edu
# 4 credits
# Description: emulating plane view
# This MP require OpenGL 3.3+. GLSL 3.3 and GLFW 3 to run
# Implementing with both vertex and fragment shaders

Compile:
make

Clean:
make clean

Control:
ESC     : quit
LEFT    : roll left
RIGHT   : roll right
UP      : pitch up
DOWN    : pitch down
P       : Pause moving
